  "title": "Senior System Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for testing, verification, integration and commissioning of system projects</li><li>Perform acceptance tests in factory and on-site</li><li>Develop system design and reviews documentation according to customer requirements</li><li>Conduct training and after-sales support to customers</li><li>Perform product demonstration to customer</li></ul><p><strong>Your qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in Electrical & Electronic, Telecommunications or Computer Engineering</li><li>Knowledge in RF, spectrum monitoring, communications networks, and/or networking experience will be given priority</li><li>Fluent in English (knowledge of other languages is an advantage)</li><li>Must be comfortable and able to handle defense and security solutions</li><li>Strong problem-solving skills as well as independent, self-motivated and result-oriented</li><li>Dedicated team player with strong job commitment</li><li>Travel (international) is required</li><li>Personnel with relevant or fitting positions will be considered for senior positions</li></ul><p>Interested candidate please forward your resume to <strong>cecilia@achievasearch.com</strong> to facilitate our discussion.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rohdeandschwarz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
